<b>Boltz 2 Is Available as a Downloadable NIM</b><br><br>




Boltz 2 is a structural biology foundation model that predicts complex biom=
olecular structures and quantifies molecular interactions. It includes supp=
ort for protein structures, nucleic acid structures, protein-nucleic acid c=
omplexes, and ligand binding and affinity prediction.<br><br>

The model supports both single molecule predictions and complex multi-molec=
ular assemblies, making it suitable for a wide range of research applicatio=
ns from basic structural biology to drug discovery.
<br><br>

