<b>NVIDIA GPU Operator v25.3.4 Is Now Available</b><br><br>




NVIDIA GPU Operator automates the lifecycle management of the software requ=
ired to expose GPUs on Kubernetes. It enables advanced functionality includ=
ing better GPU performance, utilization, and telemetry. Certified and valid=
ated for compatibility with industry-leading Kubernetes solutions, GPU Oper=
ator allows organizations to focus on building applications, rather than ma=
naging Kubernetes infrastructure.<br><br>




This release adds comprehensive support for the latest NVIDIA hardware plat=
forms: NVIDIA RTX PRO 6000 Blackwell Server Edition and NVIDIA RTX 6000D.<b=
r><br>




New capabilities include:<br>
<ul>
<li>Support for MIG Profiles</li>
<li>Support for KubeVirt/OpenShift Virtualization, enabling VMs to attach t=
o GPUs via passthrough or vGPU devices (requires vGPU v19)</li>
</ul><br>




